member.name: PWMFRect16
member.summary: The PWMFRect16 structure defines a rectangle that bounds a placeable metafile. The rectangle defines the size and position of the metafile.

member.name: PWMFRect16.Left
member.summary: Left coordinate of the rectangle that bounds the metafile.

member.name: PWMFRect16.Top
member.summary: Top coordinate of the rectangle that bounds the metafile.

member.name: PWMFRect16.Right
member.summary: Right coordinate of the rectangle that bounds the metafile.

member.name: PWMFRect16.Bottom
member.summary: Bottom coordinate of the rectangle that bounds the metafile.
